data.chText: 爱多说话的；多嘴的；饶舌的；健谈的

data.enText: He's not very talkative, is he?
She was in a talkative mood.

simple_means.memory_skill: talk 讲话 + ative 有…倾向（性质）的 → 爱说话的，健谈的

tr: friendly and open and willing to talk

example: kept from her housework by gabby neighbors

value.def: Someone who is talkative talks a lot.

example.ex: He suddenly became very talkative, his face slightly flushed, his eyes much brighter.
example.tran: 他的话突然多了起来，脸颊微微泛红，双眼明亮许多。

value.tran: 爱说话的;话多的;健谈的

rootsaffixes.indicate: 表形容词，“有…倾向（性质）的，属于…的”
rootsaffixes.title: -ative, -itive
